1.16
log
@Per POSIX, we now only require <sys/msg.h>, <sys/sem.h>, or <sys/shm.h>
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: shmat.2,v 1.15 2014/01/21 03:15:45 schwarze Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: shmat.2,v 1.2 1997/03/27 08:20:38 mikel Exp $
